      <title>Italian Jobs Are Getting Smarter</title>
      <chapter>
        <paragraph>Even if Italy is one of the last countries in the DESI 2016 ranking (DESI: "Digital Economy and Society Index" - it summarises relevant indicators on Europe’s digital performance), the use of file sharing and instant messaging tools is gradually spreading between italian workers.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>The most used communication tools are those of instant messaging and VoIP: they represent the real revolution, reducing time, allowing the connection of people and the sharing of interests and knowledges.</paragraph>
      </chapter>
